From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Sun, 1 Feb 2026 01:24:42 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: cix: Add Sky1 thermal, PWM, watchdog, and misc drivers

Add Sky1 PWM controller driver, watchdog timer driver, and CPU IPA
thermal driver. Add topology_update_freq_ref() so schedutil sees
correct max frequency when cpufreq boost is toggled. Add SCMI power
domain state verification and early init for Sky1 GPU power domain
ordering. Fix gpio_keys to respect DT-specified interrupt trigger
type for GPIO controllers without edge trigger support. Include
kernel build-install convenience script.
---
